      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Subterranean Disturbances",
        "Client": "Nearby Village\u0027s Elder",
        "Description": "We\u0027ve recently been getting\r\nearthquakes, as if something\r\nis shuffling beneath our feet.\r\nEveryone\u0027s scared and rightly\r\nso! It\u0027s hard enough trying to\r\nkeep it together when we can\r\nbarely keep things on the shelves!",
        "Target": "Hunt a Diablos",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Perturbations souterraines",
        "Client": "Ancienne du village voisin",
        "Description": "Il y a des tremblements de terre\r\ndepuis quelque temps, \u00E7a bouge\r\nsous nos pieds... Tout le monde\r\nest terrifi\u00E9 ! On tremblait d\u00E9j\u00E0\r\nbien assez comme \u00E7a, sans que\r\nnos \u00E9tag\u00E8res s\u0027y mettent aussi !",
        "Target": "Chasser un Diablos",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Disordini sotterranei",
        "Client": "Anziana (villaggio vicino)",
        "Description": "Di recente si verificano dei\r\nterremoti, come se qualcosa si\r\nmuovesse sottoterra. La gente\r\nha paura, ma come dargli\r\ntorto? \u00C8 difficile restare\r\ncalmi quando ti cade tutto\r\ndalle mensole!",
        "Target": "Caccia un Diablos",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Unterirdische Unruhe",
        "Client": "\u00C4lteste des Nachbardorfs",
        "Description": "Die Erde bebt in letzter Zeit, als\r\nw\u00FCrde etwas unter unseren F\u00FC\u00DFen\r\nverr\u00FCckt. Alle haben Angst, und\r\ndas zurecht! Es ist schwer genug,\r\nsich zusammenzurei\u00DFen, wenn um\r\nuns rum alles von den Regalen\r\ngerissen wird und auseinanderf\u00E4llt.",
        "Target": "Erjage einen Diablos.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Perturbaciones subterr\u00E1neas",
        "Client": "Anciana de aldea vecina",
        "Description": "\u00DAltimamente hay muchos\r\ntemblores, como si algo se\r\nmoviese bajo tierra. Todo\r\nel mundo teme por las extra\u00F1as\r\nnoticias de pe\u00F1as pulverizadas\r\nde la noche a la ma\u00F1ana.\r\nHay que averiguar la causa.",
        "Target": "Caza un Diablos",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
      },
      {
        "Language": "RUS",
        "Name": "\u041F\u043E\u0434\u0437\u0435\u043C\u043D\u044B\u0435 \u0442\u043E\u043B\u0447\u043A\u0438",
        "Client": "\u0421\u0442\u0430\u0440\u0435\u0439\u0448\u0438\u043D\u0430 \u0431\u043B\u0438\u0436\u043D\u0435\u0439 \u0434\u0435\u0440\u0435\u0432\u043D\u0438",
        "Description": "\u0423 \u043D\u0430\u0441 \u0441\u0435\u0439\u0447\u0430\u0441 \u043F\u043E\u0441\u0442\u043E\u044F\u043D\u043D\u044B\u0435\r\n\u0437\u0435\u043C\u043B\u0435\u0442\u0440\u044F\u0441\u0435\u043D\u0438\u044F, \u0431\u0443\u0434\u0442\u043E \u0447\u0442\u043E-\u0442\u043E\r\n\u0442\u0443\u0434\u0430-\u0441\u044E\u0434\u0430 \u0434\u0432\u0438\u0436\u0435\u0442\u0441\u044F. \u0412\u0441\u0435\r\n\u043D\u0430\u043F\u0443\u0433\u0430\u043D\u044B \u2014 \u0438 \u043D\u0435\u043C\u0443\u0434\u0440\u0435\u043D\u043E!\r\n\u041F\u043E\u043F\u0440\u043E\u0431\u0443\u0439 \u0442\u0443\u0442 \u0441\u043E\u0445\u0440\u0430\u043D\u0438\r\n\u0441\u043F\u043E\u043A\u043E\u0439\u0441\u0442\u0432\u0438\u0435!",
        "Target": "\u0412\u044B\u0441\u043B\u0435\u0434\u0438\u0442\u044C \u0414\u0438\u0430\u0431\u043B\u043E\u0441\u0430",
